      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>This fizzy purple serum tastes acidic and smells like soap. Favored by scientists, doctors, and others who work on very small scales, an ocu-amp serum greatly improves your close-range vision at the expense of your long-range vision. For 1 minute after you drink this serum, you gain a +2 circumstance on sight-based Perception checks within 30 feet and a +2 circumstance bonus to any skill use that benefits from exceedingly close vision, such as detecting complicated forgeries, performing surgery, or picking a lock. However, you take a â€“4 circumstance penalty on all sight-based Perception checks at a distance of 30 feet and greater. Additionally, anything further than 60 feet away has @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.Kjba2E3Ad5oMJ7hV.JournalEntryPage.nyB6pt2dd6iVQGmS]{concealment} from you.</p>"
